<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">I use Fire the most and heres why.<p>

A) they have a dmg shield so i don't have to waste mana casting one.<p>

B) they nuke which is sweet.<p>

C) i don't seem to notice a big difference between HP's at lower lvls (probly will change when i get higher).<p>

I play a pally as my main char and a mage and monk as my alts.  The monk i quit playing but the mage kicks a$$.  I know that when i group with a mage and they are using an earth pet, when i have a druid, ranger, me, cleric, warrior and the mage that he really sucks and is an idiot.  It bugs me that they don't know what the hell they are doing.  Then when they finally destroy their pet after me asking them to for 30 mins, they don't make a new one.  Why not? you tell me, maybe they don't wanna waste mana?<br>
Not saying that all mages suck, just the ones in my group :( but i do love them for summoning me CS's /arrows, quite handy :)<p>

40 pally <br>
16 Mage :)<br>
